{"tid":856610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又贏！中國4億隻豬或被迫「節食」","createTime":"2018-10-10T16:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T03:47:49.000Z","uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"25238b743f918bf40cfcad31a220bacf8310309f","tid":856610,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰越演越烈，中國4億隻豬或要被迫習慣一套新的飲食！據彭博報道，為了減少向外國買黃豆，中國飼料工業協會正考慮下調豬隻飼料所需的蛋白質含量。有網民就擔心，沒有蛋白質難長肉，豬農不想豬隻因而減磅，或會暗中餵食其他藥物，甚至向豬隻灌水，日後街市出售的內地豬肉或會有更多肥膏。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，中國對美國進口的黃豆課稅25%，而美國是中國最大的供應國。受此衝擊，油籽作為動物性蛋白質的主要來源，在中國價格節節高升。雖然中國已轉向巴西採購黃豆，買家亦討論與阿根廷和印度擴大貿易，但仍來不及應付今年第4季的需求，屆時中國加工廠恐怕會油籽「斷糧」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181010/58778144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58778144&d=QJHGOIQNMC%2BJSHF3LQ8HBxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=299b7029\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58778144&h=9693e6ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181010/58778144</a>"},{"pid":"052d1fedcc0284f68b01507b9ccb781588497cce","tid":856610,"uid":44105,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:19:35.000Z","msg":"中國豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起碼唔洗食草先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48426cccfe1f86f8729e60c0abffd8effb0fb46","tid":856610,"uid":89514,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:20:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"725d5220cee51df102df1cf80b651dd947068f71","tid":856610,"uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"10000億送上去<br />\n<br />\n港豬先要「節食」"},{"pid":"5742d5323746ce00d2b8b81534311088275d74a7","tid":856610,"uid":82155,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedB